msgctxt "56"
msgid "You there... Halt."
msgstr "alto, espera."

msgctxt "68"
msgid "What's cracking, old man?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "80"
msgid "My name is not \"old man.\" I am Sotaro Komaki, a master of the most esoteric martial arts known to man."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "92"
msgid "O...kay. And what do you want with me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "104"
msgid "Simply put, I can sense one's physical ability merely by observing the gait of their walk. And you, my suave friend, appear to be an especially promising specimen."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "116"
msgid "Hold up, you're not trying to get me to join some kinda kooky dojo, are you? That stuff's not really my style."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "128"
msgid "You needn't join anything. Take this."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "140"
msgid "You got a <Color:8>Memo<Color:Default>."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "152"
msgid "Read <Color:14>memos<Color:Default> by selecting <Color:14>Memos<Color:Default> in the Pause Menu. Access the Pause Menu with the <Action:Button_Options@Adventure> button.\r\n\r\nYou will collect <Color:14>memos<Color:Default> as you progress through the story and interact with people in the city."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "164"
msgid "<Color:14>Memos<Color:Default> cover a wide variety of topics, all of which will be useful for life in Kamurocho. Explore the city top to bottom to complete your <Color:14>memo<Color:Default> collection!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "176"
msgid "Any information you glean from these memos will not only grant you knowledge but worldly experience. Now go forth, and let your brain soak up information like the sponge it is!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "188"
msgid "...Sure. Thanks, old man."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "212"
msgid "You gained 500 EXP."
msgstr ""

